---
/** Link de pago Mercado Pago (monto libre). */
const MP_LINK = "https://link.mercadopago.com.ar/pasochilehoy";
---

<div class="support-block">
  <div class="support-text">
    <p class="support-title">¿Te fue útil?</p>
    <p class="support-desc">
      Este proyecto es independiente y gratuito. Si te ayudó a planificar tu viaje, podés apoyar su
      desarrollo con lo que quieras.
    </p>
  </div>
  <a
    href={MP_LINK}
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="support-btn"
    aria-label="Apoyar el proyecto vía Mercado Pago"
  >
    <svg
      width="16"
      height="16"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <path
        d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"
      ></path>
    </svg>
    Apoyar el proyecto
  </a>
</div>

<style>
  .support-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(91, 174, 255, 0.04), rgba(200, 121, 65, 0.04));
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .support-block {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  .support-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .support-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .support-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .support-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 9px 18px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    border: 1px solid rgba(91, 174, 255, 0.3);
    background: rgba(91, 174, 255, 0.06);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition:
      background var(--transition-fast),
      border-color var(--transition-fast);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .support-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(91, 174, 255, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(91, 174, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .support-btn:active {
    transform: scale(0.97);
  }
</style>
